text: Akari Inaba (born 2 February 1998) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2018 Asian Games, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * "Akari Inaba of Japan throws during the Women's Water Polo..."
